Name: Logitech Driving Force Shifter for G29 & G920
Description:
Upgrade your racing sim setup for an immersive experience.

The Logitech Driving Force Shifter is a sim racing shifter that can be used with the G923, G29, and G920 racing wheels. It is designed for precision and reliability, and is built for long-lasting reliability and precision racing. 

The shifter has a six-speed short-throw gearbox, a solid steel gear shaft, and a leather knob and boot. It also features a six-speed “H” pattern gearbox and leather and steel components. 

The shifter is designed to enhance the racing experience by adding realistic shifting action to a racing rig. It is also compatible with the latest PC and console racing titles.

Name: Finish Classic Tablet 110 Pack
Description:
Finish Classic Tablet 110 Pack

Condition: Brand New

Directions
Usage Instructions:
1) Remove food scraps and scrape plates and dishes.
2) Load dishes with soiled surfaces facing water spray.
3) Unwrap one tablet and place in the dry dispenser. For short cycles (30 minutes), IF IT DOES NOT FIT IN THE DISPENSER or does not dissolve properly, place it in the bottom of the dishwasher and choose a cycle with no pre-rinse. FOR A FISHER & PAYKEL DISHDRAWER®, if it does not fit in the dispenser, place tablet in an empty section of the cutlery basket.
4) For best performance it is recommended to use the "normal" wash cycle or a specialist tablet wash cycle. Suitable for most septic tanks, however refer to manufacturer of your wastewater treatment system for septic advice. We recommend using Finish Rinse Aid for best drying and shine results.
USAGE ADVICE

Try the Finish System
Finish Classic + Finish Rinse Aid

And for a clean machine we recommend:
Finish Dishwasher Cleaner + Finish Freshener
STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store Classic tablets in a dry and cool place, away from heat and moisture.

Name: Women's Lightweight Unity Fitz Wildrise Crew
Description:
Women's Lightweight Unity Fitz Wildrise Crew

Condition: Brand New

The artwork for our Unity Fitz styles has a stylized Earth and the message "we're all on this together," plus the gist of our purpose statement "save our home planet." Textile waste is a global problem, so our Wildrise styles are made from a blend of post-industrial recycled cotton and Naia® Renew (a mix of renewable wood pulp and postconsumer plastics). Soft, comfortable and built to last, this lightweight crewneck sweatshirt is warm and versatile for year-round wear. Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory.

Features:
Made with Recycled Materials.
Classic Crew.
Rib-Knit Trim.
Supporting the People Who Made This Product.
Country Of Origin
Made in Mexico.

Material:

Care Instructions: Machine Wash Cold, Do Not Bleach, Tumble Dry Low, Cool Iron.

Locker Loop
Tagless Design

Women's Unity Fitz Easy-Cut Responsibili-Tee®

Condition: New Brand

The artwork for our Unity Fitz styles has a stylized Earth and the message "we're all on this together," plus the gist of our purpose statement "save our home planet." It's printed on a T-shirt built with 100% recycled fabric that reduces our reliance on virgin raw materials. Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory.

Features
100% Recycled Fabric
Versatile Crewneck
Boxy Tee
Supporting the People Who Made This Product
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory, which means the people who made this product earned a premium for their labor
Country Of Origin
Made in Mexico.

Material:
5.4-oz 50% recycled cotton/50% postconsumer recycled polyester jersey
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory
Care Instructions: Machine Wash Cold, Do Not Bleach, Tumble Dry Low, Cool Iron

Name: Patagonia Women's Long-Sleeved Work Pocket T-Shirt
Description:
Patagonia Women's Long-Sleeved Work Pocket T-Shirt

Condition: New Brand

A sturdy and comfortable long-sleeved pocket tee for hard work, built with a breathable blend of 55% industrial hemp/45% organic cotton jersey. Rib-knit cuffs resist stretching out of shape and keep fabric out of work’s way when you push up your sleeves to get the job done. Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory.

Features:
Durable, Breathable and Comfortable Construction
Left-Chest Pocket with Patagonia® Workwear P-6 Logo
Rib-Knit Cuffs
Supporting the People Who Made This Product
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory, which means the people who made this product earned a premium for their labor
Country Of Origin
Made in Sri Lanka.

Material:
Body: 6.6-oz 55% industrial hemp/45% organic cotton jersey
Collar and cuffs: 9.7-oz 53% industrial hemp/42% organic cotton/5% spandex rib knit
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory
Care Instructions: Machine Wash Warm, Do Not Bleach, Tumble Dry Low, Warm Iron

Name: Patagonia Women's Happy Hike Studio Pants
Description:
Patagonia Women's Happy Hike Studio Pants

Condition: New Brand

These versatile pants with a 26½" inseam now have a slimmer fit, a wide waistband, knit cuffs and a secure right-thigh pocket. They're made of lightweight 89% recycled polyester/11% spandex stretch-woven fabric for comfort and freedom of movement. Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory.

Features:
Lightweight, Stretchy Fabric
Flattering Waistband
Pocket Details
Two front drop-in pockets with tonal double-needle stitch detail, two back pockets (one with a secure zipper), and one zippered right-thigh pocket
Push-Up Cuffs
Knit ankle cuffs can be pushed up to the calves
Now a Slimmer Fit
Mid-rise with a regular fit that's slimmer than previous seasons and has tapered legs; if you purchased these awhile back, size up when buying this slimmer version
Supporting the People Who Made This Product
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory, which means the people who made this product earned a premium for their labor
Country Of Origin
Made in Vietnam.

Material:
Body: 5-oz 89% recycled polyester/11% spandex stretch plain weave with a DWR (durable water repellent) finish
Waistband and cuffs: 6.3-oz 81% NetPlus® postconsumer recycled nylon made from recycled fishing nets to help reduce ocean plastic pollution/19% spandex knit with miDori™ bioSoft for added wicking and softness, and HeiQ® Pure odor control
DWR finish is made without PFCs (perfluorinated chemicals)
Waistband/cuff fabric is certified as bluesign® approved
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory
Care Instructions: Machine Wash Warm, Do Not Bleach, Tumble Dry Low, Cool Iron

Name: Patagonia Women's Nano-Air® Light Bottoms
Description:
Patagonia Women's Nano-Air® Light Bottoms

Condition: New Brand

Unlike any midlayer bottoms you've ever worn, the Nano-Air® Light Bottoms blend the benefits of insulated tights and pants. They deliver warm, stretchy and breathable performance for moving fast in cold climates. Inseam is 28". Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory.

Features:
Breathable, Stretchy Fabric
Revolutionary Insulation
Stretch Panels for Added Mobility
Harness Compatible
Pocket Features
One right-thigh pocket with a low-profile invisible zipper stores small items securely while on the move
Cuff Features
Cuffs feature quick-drying recycled nylon/spandex knit for enhanced stretch and movement, and push up easily to stretch over or tuck into alpine boots
Supporting the People Who Made This Product
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory, which means the people who made this product earned a premium for their labor
Country Of Origin
Made in Vietnam.

Material:
Shell and lining: 1.6-oz 30-denier 100% recycled polyester air-permeable shadow stretch ripstop with a durable water repellent (DWR) finish made without perfluorinated chemicals (PFCs/PFAS)
Waistband and cuffs: 5.8-oz 74% NetPlus® postconsumer recycled nylon made from recycled fishing nets to help reduce ocean plastic pollution/26% spandex Technostretch knit with miDori™ bioSoft for added wicking and softness, and HeiQ® Pure odor control
Panels: 6.5-oz 91% recycled polyester/9% spandex flat-faced Technostretch fleece
Insulation: 40-g FullRange® 100% polyester (93% recycled)
Waistband and cuff fabric is certified as bluesign® approved
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory
Care Instructions: Machine Wash Warm, Do Not Bleach, Tumble Dry Low, Cool Iron

Name: Patagonia Women's SnowDrifter Bibs
Description:
Patagonia Women's SnowDrifter Bibs

Condition: New Brand

Our lightweight SnowDrifter Bibs combine recycled, 3-layer stretch fabric with a minimalist design for H2No® Performance Standard protection in even the stormiest conditions and breathable, unrestrictive performance on the skintrack. Fabric, membrane and DWR finish are made without perfluorinated chemicals (PFCs/PFAS). Inseam length is 32". Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory.

Specs & Features
Light, Stretchy, Storm-Ready Fabric
Soft, Comfortable Suspenders
Drop-Seat Design
Hardworking Gaiters
Three Zip-Secured Pockets
Built-In RECCO® Reflector; Inseam Length
Supporting the People Who Made This Product
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory, which means the people who made this product earned a premium for their labor
Country Of Origin
Made in Vietnam.

Material:
H2No® Performance Standard shell: 3-layer, 4.3-oz 50-denier 100% recycled polyester stretch plain weave with a soft recycled polyester knit backer and a DWR (durable water repellent) finish
Bib upper: 7.7-oz 89% recycled polyester certified by OceanCycle and sourced from coastal communities at risk of plastic pollution/11% XLANCE® stretch double weave; with a DWR finish
Fabric, membrane and DWR finish are made without PFCs (perfluorinated chemicals)
Bib upper fabric is certified as bluesign® approved
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory
Care Instructions: Machine Wash Warm, Do Not Bleach, Tumble Dry Low, Cool Iron

Women's Terrebonne Joggers

Condition: New Brand

Add a pair of lightweight performance pants to your trail kit with the Terrebonne Joggers: light, breathable, quick-drying and stretchy, with a comfortable waistband and cuffs, and a durable water repellent (DWR) finish made without perfluorinated chemicals (PFCs/PFAS). They’re perfect for any activity on the trail. Inseam length is 28". Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory.

Features:
Stretchy Fabric
Slim-Fit Jogger with 28" Inseam
Adjustable Waistband
Pockets for Storage
Hemostat/Carabiner Loop
Articulated Knees
Articulated shaping at the knees offers range of motion
Supporting the People Who Made This Product
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory, which means the people who made this product earned a premium for their labor
Country Of Origin
Made in Vietnam.

Material:
Body: 2.5-oz 90% recycled polyester certified by OceanCycle and sourced from coastal communities at risk of plastic pollution/10% spandex stretch plain weave; with a durable water repellent (DWR) finish made without perfluorinated chemicals (PFCs/PFAS)
Pocket bags: 2.1-oz 100% recycled polyester tricot mesh
Body fabric is certified as bluesign® approved
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory
Care Instructions: Machine Wash Warm, Do Not Bleach, Tumble Dry Low, Cool Iron

Name: Patagonia Women's Upstride Pants
Description:
Patagonia Women's Upstride Pants

Condition: New Brand

The lightweight Upstride Pants are designed to go uphill fast. Built of a breathable, recycled stretch-knit face fabric with a PFC-free DWR finish (durable water repellent coating that does not contain perfluorinated chemicals), they excel on long, high-output tours in predictable weather. Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory.

Features:
Stretchy, Highly-Breathable Fabric
Clean, Simple Waist
Two Zip-Secured Pockets
Two secure zippered cargo pockets
Hardworking Cuffs
Gaiters seal out snow; tough scuff guards protect inside of legs and bottom hem; three-setting snap adjustment and zipper at bottom cuffs
Built-In RECCO® Reflector
Concealed RECCO® reflector
Supporting the People Who Made This Product
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory, which means the people who made this product earned a premium for their labor
Country Of Origin
Made in Vietnam.

Material:
Body: 6.9-oz 100% recycled polyester stretch-knit face fabric bonded to an embossed polyester backer with a PFC-free DWR finish (durable water repellent coating that does not contain perfluorinated chemicals)
Waistband: 6.1-oz 75% recycled nylon/25% spandex knit with miDori™ bioSoft for added wicking and softness, and HeiQ® Pure odor control
Waistband fabric is certified as bluesign® approved
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory
Care Instructions: Machine Wash Warm, Do Not Bleach, Tumble Dry Low, Cool Iron

Name: Patagonia Women's Quandary Joggers
Description:
Patagonia Women's Quandary Joggers

Condition: New Brand

The classic Quandary Pants, now in a jogger silhouette. These multifunctional hiking pants are made of 96% NetPlus® postconsumer recycled nylon made from recycled fishing nets to help reduce ocean plastic pollution/4% spandex plain weave; with a durable water repellent (DWR) finish made without perfluorinated chemicals (PFCs/PFAS) to resist light moisture, and 40+ UPF sun protection. The inseam is 28".

Features:
Light, Technical Fabric Blend
Waistband Details
The lie-flat, knit waistband with an external drawcord provides a soft, snug fit and is treated with miDori™ bioSoft for added wicking and softness, and HeiQ® Pure odor control to keep things fresh
Pockets Hold Essentials
Two front pockets, two zippered thigh pockets, and one back-right pocket
Built for Mobility
Articulation on the calves boosts mobility
Hemostat/Carabiner Loop
Reinforced hemostat/carabiner loop on the front-right pocket
Cinched Cuffs; 28" Inseam
Elasticated cuffs lend stylish versatility; inseam length is 28"
Country Of Origin
Made in Vietnam.

Material:
Body: 4.4-oz 96% NetPlus® postconsumer recycled nylon made from recycled fishing nets to help reduce ocean plastic pollution/4% spandex plain weave with a durable water repellent (DWR) finish made without perfluorinated chemicals (PFCs/PFAS), and 40+ UPF sun protection
Waistband: 6.3-oz 80% recycled nylon/20% spandex knit with miDori™ bioSoft for added wicking and softness, and HeiQ® Pure odor control
Fabrics are certified as bluesign® approved
Care Instructions: Machine Wash Warm, Do Not Bleach, Tumble Dry Low, Cool Iron

Name: Patagonia Women's Torrentshell 3L Rain Pants - Regular
Description:
Patagonia Women's Torrentshell 3L Rain Pants - Regular

Condition: New Brand

Simple and unpretentious, our trusted Torrentshell 3L Rain Pants meet Patagonia’s H2No® Performance Standard for exceptional waterproof/breathable performance. Torrentshell provides all-day comfort and long-lasting waterproof durability, and these 3-layer pants contain fabric, membrane and DWR finish that are made without perfluorinated chemicals (PFCs/PFAS). Inseam is 32"; also available in 30" inseam. Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory.

Features:
100% Recycled Waterproof/Breathable Face Fabric
Pocket Features
Two handwarmer pockets have mesh pocket bags and storm flaps
Cuff-to-Thigh Side Zips
Welted, two-way side zips extend from cuffs to thighs for easy pull-on over boots and they double as vents; partially elasticized cuffs adjust with a snap-tab closure
Inseam Lengths
Inseam is 32"; also available in 30" inseam
Supporting the People Who Made This Product
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory, which means the people who made this product earned a premium for their labor
Country Of Origin
Made in Vietnam.

Material:
H2No® Performance Standard shell made without perfluorinated chemicals (fabrics, membrane and finishes made without PFCs/PFAS): 3-layer, 3.5-oz 50-denier ECONYL® 100% recycled nylon ripstop face, a polycarbonate PU membrane with 13% biobased content, a tricot backer and a DWR finish
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory
Care Instructions: Machine Wash Warm, Do Not Bleach, Tumble Dry Low, Cool Iron

Men's P-6 Logo Responsibili-Tee®

A classic graphic on a T-shirt made with recycled fabrics. By utilizing fabric scraps and recycled bottles, this tee reduces our reliance on virgin raw materials. Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory.

100% Recycled Fabric
Versatile Crewneck
Built for Comfort and Fit
Hem Details
This T-shirt has a straight hem and can be worn tucked or untucked
Supporting the People Who Made This Product

Country Of Origin
Made in Mexico.

5.5-oz 50% recycled cotton/50% postconsumer recycled polyester jersey
Fabric is certified as bluesign® approved
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory

Name: Patagonia Men's Capilene® Cool Daily Shirt
Description:
Patagonia Men's Capilene® Cool Daily Shirt

Condition: New Brand

Our most versatile technical top is built for use on the trail or on the water: It’s quick drying, has stretch for mobility and comfort, plus HeiQ® Mint odor control. Made with 50-100% recycled polyester, Capilene® Cool Daily styles keep you comfortable when you’re working hard in conditions ranging from cool to hot. Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory.

Features:
Set-In Sleeve Construction
Light, Soft and Forgiving fabric
Stretch fabric provides enhanced comfort during activities both in and out of water
Built-In Wicking and Odor Control
Fabric has a wicking finish and HeiQ® Mint odor control for long-lasting freshness
Designed with Minimal Seams
Minimal stitching and seams to help reduce chafing
Supporting the People Who Made This Product
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory, which means the people who made this product earned a premium for their labor
Country Of Origin
Made in Indonesia.

Material:
Solids: 3.7-oz 100% recycled polyester (heathers and cross-dyes: 50% recycled) jersey with HeiQ® Mint odor control and a wicking finish
Made in a Fair Trade Certified™ factory
Care Instructions: Machine Wash Warm, Do Not Bleach, Tumble Dry Low, Cool Iron, Do Not Use Fabric Softeners

Name: Patagonia Men's Quandary Joggers
Description:
Patagonia Men's Quandary Joggers

Condition: New Brand

The classic Quandary Pants, now in a jogger silhouette. These multifunctional hiking pants are built of 96% NetPlus® postconsumer recycled nylon made from recycled fishing nets to help reduce ocean plastic pollution/4% spandex plain weave; with a durable water repellent (DWR) finish made without perfluorinated chemicals (PFCs/PFAS) to resist light moisture, and 40+ UPF sun protection. Inseam length is 30".

Features:
Light, Technical Fabric Blend
Waistband Details
Elasticized waistband with a faux fly and an external drawcord for a soft, snug fit
Pockets Hold Essentials
Built for Mobility
Articulation on the calves boosts mobility
Hemostat/Carabiner Loop
Reinforced hemostat/carabiner loop on the front-right pocket
Cinched Cuffs; 30" Inseam
Elasticized cuffs lend stylish versatility; inseam length is 30"
UPF Testing Methods and Details
This product has been tested in accordance with Australian/New Zealand test methods AS/NZS 4399 or AATCC 183 or EN 13758. Only covered areas are protected. The protection offered by this item may be reduced with use or if stretched or wet
Country Of Origin
Made in Vietnam.

Material:
4.4-oz 96% NetPlus® postconsumer recycled nylon made from recycled fishing nets to help reduce ocean plastic pollution/4% spandex plain weave; with a durable water repellent (DWR) finish made without perfluorinated chemicals (PFCs/PFAS), and 40+ UPF sun protection
Fabric is certified as bluesign® approved
Care Instructions: Machine Wash Warm, Do Not Bleach, Tumble Dry Low, Cool Iron

Made from Kankens signature Vinylon F material, this hip pack is designed with durability in mind. This material is also water-resistant, making it easy to wipe off water droplets if you get caught in a shower. Keep your small, frequently accessed essentials in either the front or rear external pockets.

Name: Delta By Delta Goodrem Eau de Parfum 30ml
Description:
Delta By Delta Goodrem Eau de Parfum 30ml

Condition: Brand New

General Information
Australian pop icon Delta Goodrem introduces her first foray into the fragrance world with her debut scent, Delta by Delta Goodrem. Launching in Australia this April 2017, the fragrance exudes femininity and boho elegance, a perfect reflection of Delta's charm and character.

"Launching my very own signature perfume is the realization of a dream come true. These last few years have been such a creative time for me, personally and professionally and it has given me a sense of empowerment as a woman.

"For me, this fragrance embodies the spirit of all this special time. It's fun, feminine and fresh. I want the perfume to represent the girls and women who wear it. Perfume is such a dynamic addition to anyone's life and beauty routine. It's the finishing touch to any outfit, performance and sets us on the adventure in our day". Delta says.

Opening with notes of juicy mandarin, velvety nectarine and bright green apple, the scent's top notes are infused with vivacious energy and sparkle. The heart of the fragrance shares Delta's joyous style with a hint of sweet honeysuckle that mingles harmoniously with jasmine pearls and wild orchid. Rooted in the background are ingredients that lay close to skin with the softest touch including creamy sandalwood and warm vanilla wrapped in a white musk to embody  pure luxury.

The refined bottle showcases the simple elegance and style that Delta is known for, featuring weighted glass and adorned with luxe gold filigree feathers - the perfect addition to any woman's fragrance collection.

Name: Allbirds Men's Tree Runner
Description:
Allbirds Men's Tree Runner

Condition: Brand New

Our breathable, silky-smooth sneaker made with responsibly sourced eucalyptus tree fiber treads lightly in everything you do.

Best For: Walking, warmer weather, everyday wear

Thermoregulating Material: Lightweight, breathable eucalyptus fiber provides next-level comfort

Versatile Design: Wear-with-everything classic style, great for travel

Care Guide
1. Remove the laces and insoles.

2. Place shoes in a delicates bag (pro tip: a pillowcase works too).

3. Choose a gentle cycle with cold water & mild detergent.

4. Shake out any excess water & set aside to air dry.

5. Shoes will regain their original shape with one or two wears.

Name: Allbirds Men's Tree Dasher 2
Description:
Allbirds Men's Tree Dasher 2

Condition: Brand New

Men's Tree Dasher 2 Highlights
Seamless one-piece upper provides maximum comfort
Lightly padded heel collar locks ankle in place
Flexible, cushioned midsole offers a smoother ride

Details:
The Tree Dasher 2 is the next evolution of our everyday active shoe with more responsive foam, extra grip, and an improved fit to keep you moving, and nature winning.

Best For: Everyday walks, jogs, and light workouts.

No-Slip Heel Fit: Improved heel collar helps lock ankle in place.

A Cushier Crash Pad: Sportier, angular heel shape softens impact.

Easy Slip-On Design: Single-piece knit upper makes getting out and staying active effortless.

Heel Drop: 7mm (Forefoot: 15.5mm, Heel: 22.5mm)

Weight: 289.99 g

Care Guide:
Remove the laces and insoles.
Place shoes in a delicates bag (pro tip: a pillowcase works too).
Choose a gentle cycle with cold water & mild detergent.
Shake out any excess water & set aside to air dry.
Shoes will regain their original shape with one or two wears.
Handy tips: Don’t put them in the dryer. They’ll go back to their original shape in no time. You can hand wash your laces and insoles on their own.

Name: Allbirds Men's Wool Runner 2
Description:
Allbirds Men's Wool Runner 2

Condition: Brand New

Men's Wool Runner 2 Highlights
Enhanced comfort thanks to 14% more foam under your foot and a roomier toe-box
Improved durability with an upper that provides reinforcements to help prevent toe poke-through

Details:

Upper made with ZQ Merino Wool: An upper that’s so soft and cozy, you can wear them all day and still not want to take them off when you get home.

Increased Durability: A more uniform all-around structure that will help maintain your shoe’s shape over time, while preventing toe poke-through.

3. Choose a gentle cycle with cold water & mild detergent.

4. Shake out any excess water & set aside to air dry.

5. Shoes will regain their original shape with one or two wears.

Name: Allbirds Men's Trail Runner SWT
Description:
Allbirds Men's Trail Runner SWT

Condition: Brand New

Men's Trail Runner SWT Highlights
Sturdy outsole grips hiking trails
Tear-resistant ripstop mudguard protects feet from tough terrain
Snug, sock-like collar blocks debris

Details:
Explore new places with our first-ever hiking & trail running shoe. Tested for durability, stability, and traction, it’s the trainer, comfort, and sustainability you love with new ripstop fabric, grippy treads, and stabilising support to take on any adventure.

Best For: Hiking, walking and trail running

Natural Innovation: Durable, water-resistant finish helps keep shoes from getting soggy

All-Condition Traction: Multi-directional 4mm lugs perform on any terrain

Care Guide:
Remove the laces and insoles.
Place shoes in a delicates bag (pro tip: a pillowcase works too).
Choose a gentle cycle with cold water & mild detergent.
Shake out any excess water & set aside to air dry.
Shoes will regain their original shape with one or two wears.
Handy tips: Don’t put them in the dryer. They’ll go back to their original shape in no time. You can hand wash your laces and insoles on their own.

Please note: Shoes are in US sizing

Name: Allbirds Men's Wool Dasher 2 Mizzle
Description:
Allbirds Men's Wool Dasher 2 Mizzle

Condition: Brand New

Men's Wool Dasher 2 Mizzle Highlights:
Water-repellent Puddle Guard® technology keeps feet dry
All-condition traction grips slippery surfaces
Reflective details increase visibility for safer mornings and evenings

Details
Take cold and wet weather in stride with the active shoe that uses natural materials to give you extra grip and keep your feet cozy when the forecast is gloomy.

Best For: Wet-weather Walks, jogs, and runs.

Natural Innovation: Durable, water-repellent finish helps keep shoes from getting soggy.

Cushioned Comfort: Flexible, soft midsole offers a smoother ride.

Easy Slip-On Design: Single-piece knit upper makes getting out and staying active effortless.

Heel Drop: 7mm (Forefoot: 15.5mm, Heel: 22.5mm)

Care Guide
To preserve the Mizzle’s fluorine-free water-repellent treatment, we recommend spot cleaning with warm water and gentle soap whenever possible. If they need a deep clean, follow the below steps to machine wash, but only on a limited basis.

Remove the laces and insoles.
Place shoes in a delicates bag (pro tip: a pillowcase works too).
Choose a gentle cycle with cold water & mild detergent.
Shake out any excess water & set aside to air dry.
Shoes will regain their original shape with one or two wears.

Please note: Shoes are in US sizing

Name: Allbirds Women's Tree Runner
Description:
Allbirds Women's Tree Runner

Condition: Brand New

Women's Tree Runner Highlights
Lightweight, breathable eucalyptus fibre provides next-level comfort
Cushioned midsole gives wear-all-day support
Machine-washable materials keep shoes looking like new

Details
Our breathable, silky-smooth sneaker made with responsibly sourced eucalyptus tree fibre treads lightly in everything you do.

Best For: Walking, warmer weather, everyday wear

Thermoregulating Material: Lightweight, breathable eucalyptus fibre provides next-level comfort

Versatile Design: Wear-with-everything classic style, great for travel

Care Guide
1. Remove the laces and insoles.

2. Place shoes in a delicates bag (pro tip: a pillowcase works too).

3. Choose a gentle cycle with cold water & mild detergent.

4. Shake out any excess water & set aside to air dry.

5. Shoes will regain their original shape with one or two wears.

Name: Allbirds Women's Tree Flyer 2
Description:
Allbirds Women's Tree Flyer 2

Condition: Brand New

Women's Tree Flyer 2 Highlights
Running shoe helps propel you and the planet forward
Same spring you love, with increased traction, stability, and support
Bouncy SwiftFoam™ cushions every step

Best For: Running, training, fitness classes, home/gym workouts

Stabilizing, Sustainable Design: External heel counter (made entirely of recycled content from the midsole foaming process) helps keep your strides steady and reduces waste.

Extra Support: Bio TPU overlays on the toe and midfoot adds stability, durability, and lateral support.

Place shoes in a delicates bag (pro tip: a pillowcase works too).

Shake out any excess water & set aside to air dry.
Shoes will regain their original shape with one or two wears.

Simply use in the shower as the first step in your three-step acne routine, washing your chest and back (but you can also use it on your face): wet the area you want to cleanse, work into a lather, apply then leave for 30 seconds before washing off and patting dry. Start off using Benzac AC Moderate Strength 5% Acne Wash once daily, before working up to twice-daily applications. During the first weeks of treatment, a sudden increase in peeling will occur in most people; this will normally subside within a day or two if treatment is temporarily stopped.

colour*.

bounces back for an even, natural shine.

pour it into the developer bottle. Secure and close the applicator tip and shake to

rinse.

minutes, then rinse thoroughly.

Name: fLASH Amplifying Eyelash Serum 2ml
Description:

Condition: Brand New

Product Description
fLASH Amplifying Eyelash Serum is an amplifying eyelash serum designed to give you long, beautiful lashes.

The highly concentrated serum delivers benefits that you will begin to notice within a couple of weeks. And with its once-daily application, it’s simple too!

Dosage:

Thanks to the high concentration of fLASH™, with one application daily, you will achieve the most beautiful eyes and a look expressive and impressive in a few weeks.

How to apply fLASH™?


fLASH™ is applied over clean, dry skin. Wait 2-3 minutes for the product to dry before using any other cosmetic product. Take the applicator tube and clean the excess product on the upper edge of the tube. Product application starts on the outer eye corner, sliding the applicator over the skin of the upper eyelid, on the base of the lash line. Do the same over the skin of the lower eyelid, on the base of the lash line. In just 2-3 weeks you will start to notice a difference in your lashes. But, with continued use of fLASH™, in 6 to 12 weeks you will get the full benefits. If this is your first time using fLASH™, you must apply it every other day for the first week. From the second week, use fLASH™ daily for about six weeks or until you have the desired length in your lashes. Once your desired length is achieved, reduce the use of fLASH™ to 2 or 3 times a week.

Apply to clean, dry underarms. Reapply throughout the day for best results. Patch-test before use.

New to natural deodorants? Not sure how they work?

If you're new to essano's natural deodorants, your body might go through a readjustment phase, which takes up to 30 days for your body to adjust fully from aluminium-based deodorants and antiperspirants.

During this readjustment phase, you can sometimes experience an increase of odour-causing bacteria. But rest assured that this won't last forever as it is just a part of the adjustment that happens when your pores are no longer blocked.

Once your body completed the readjustment phase, the bacteria and odour will subside and you can be confident you are using a product that is gentle yet effective.
